{%- comment -%}

This snippet renders the map background associated with the given map item.

Args:
  map: the collection map item

Renders:
  relative url of the map background image corresponding to the map background set for the given map item

{%- endcomment -%}
{%- assign rmb_backgroundEntry = site.data.backgrounds | where: "background", include.map.background | first %}
{%- include renderBackground.liquid backgroundEntry=rmb_backgroundEntry -%}